<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Request Submitted - Brandeis University Open Access Fund</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/brandeis.png">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/public/brandeis.png">
  <style>
    :root { 
      --radius: 16px; 
      --brandeis-blue: #123374;
      --brandeis-light-blue: #4a90e2;
      --brandeis-gray: #666;
      --success-green: #28a745;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { height: 100%; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: #fff;
      color: #333;
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Main Content */
    .main-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      width: min(820px, 100%);
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .card h1 { 
      margin: 0 0 8px; 
      font-size: 2rem; 
      color: var(--brandeis-blue);
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .card .subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      color: var(--brandeis-gray);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* Success Icon */
    .success-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      background: var(--success-green);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Success Message */
    .success-message {
      background: #d4edda;
      border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
      color: #155724;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .success-message h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #155724;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .success-message p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .success-message ul {
      margin: 10px 0 0 20px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .success-message li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    /* Action Buttons */
    .action-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      min-width: 140px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--brandeis-blue);
      color: white;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--brandeis-light-blue);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: var(--brandeis-blue);
      border: 2px solid var(--brandeis-blue);
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--brandeis-blue);
      color: white;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
      <h1>Request Submitted Successfully!</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Your Open Access Fund request has been received</p>
      
      <div class="success-message">
        <h3>What happens next?</h3>
        <p>Thank you for submitting your Open Access Fund request. Here's what you can expect:</p>
        <ul>
          <!-- <li>You will receive a confirmation email shortly with your request details</li> -->
          <li>Our library publishing team will review your request within 3-5 business days</li>
          <li>You will be notified of the decision via email</li>
          <li>If approved, funding will be processed according to your publication timeline</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="https://oafund.library.brandeis.edu/upload" class="btn btn-primary">Upload Documents</a>
        <a href="https://www.brandeis.edu/library/" class="btn btn-secondary">Return to Library</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>